A test run of this EBG808 #MatonCustomShop Acoustic at @theacousticcentre (South Melbourne, Australia). Featuring an Adirondack Spruce top, figured Australian Blackwood back & sides, a Mahogany neck, Ebony fretboard and gorgeous Abalone purfling. This model includes the iconic Maton 'keyhole' headstock, along with the impeccable AP5-Pro pickup system.

The signature guitar of guitar maestro @michaelfix_official, the Maton EBG808C MICFIX at @cranbournemusic (Melbourne, Australia)!
The combination of a “AAA” Sitka Spruce soundboard, Ebony fingerboard & bridge and solid Queensland Maple back, sides & neck produce a tone that is rich, full and well balanced, with the glassy highs essential to Michael’s tone.

Stunning photos of #21 of the Vera May Special at @mooloolabamusic (Minyama, QLD, Australia). Featuring a “AAA” Grade Lutz Spruce Face, “AA” Grade Blackwood Back & Sides, Blackwood Neck and Streaky Ebony Fingerboard & Bridge. This contemporary take on our traditional W.A May Headstock consists of Blackwood Sides with an Ebony Wedge.
